---
alwaysApply: true
apply:
  - "**/*.py"
  - "**/*.sh"
  - "**/*.yml"
  - "**/*.yaml"
  - "**/*.toml"
---

Always use the virtual environment for this project.

The virtual environment is located in the root of the project and is called `.venv`.

The virtual environment is created using the `.venv` module.

The virtual environment is activated using the `source .venv/bin/activate` command.

The virtual environment is deactivated using the `deactivate` command.
